 MAXPutFile()

 Function: Sends commands to DoorRunner via a text file.

 Returns:  FALSE -> Error (Couldn't open file)

 Note:     NOT CALLED BY YOUR PROGRAM DIRECTLY

@endnode

@node "E2" ""
@next "E3"
@prev "E1"

 MAXGetFile()

 Function: Receives return values from DoorRunner via a text file.

 Returns:  FALSE -> Error (Couldn't open file)

 Note:     NOT CALLED BY YOUR PROGRAM DIRECTLY

@endnode

@node "E3" ""
@next "E4"
@prev "E2"

 MAXWaitPort()

 Function: Waits for DoorRunner to write to text file then exits.

 Returns:  FALSE -> Error
           TRUE  -> Ok

 Note:     NOT CALLED BY YOUR PROGRAM DIRECTLY

@endnode

@node "E4" ""
@next "E5"
