 MAXSendMessage(message:PTR TO CHAR, linefeed:LONG)

 Function: Prints message to Local Screen & Modem.

 Inputs:   message  - The message you want to be printed (MAX 80 chars)
           linefeed - 1 if you want a terminating CR/LF sequence

 Returns:  FALSE -> Error
           0     -> Ok
           1     -> User Broke with ^C

@endnode

@node "E7" ""
@next "E8"
@prev "E6"

 MAXSendScreen(message:PTR TO CHAR, linefeed:LONG)

 Function: Prints message to Local Screen only.

 Inputs    message  - The message you want to be printed (MAX 80 chars)
           linefeed - 1 if you want a terminating CR/LF sequence

 Returns:  FALSE -> Error
           0     -> Ok
           1     -> User Broke with ^C

@endnode

