 MAXGetString(message:PTR TO CHAR, maxchars:LONG, buffer:PTR TO CHAR)

 Function: Prints message to Local Screen & Modem and prompts for input
           from user.

 Inputs:   message  - The message you want to be printed (MAX 80 chars)
           maxchars - Number of chars user can enter (MAX 80 chars)
           buffer   - a buffer that gets filled with what the user enters

 Returns:  Nothing

@endnode

